name: Wat Tyler Country Park Orchard
description: The park features a traditional orchard area with heritage apples and pears, managed for education and public picking.

name: Vange Creek Samphire
short_description: Salt marsh greens near the creek.
description: Marsh samphire and sea aster can be found on the tidal mudflats of the Vange Creek and marshes.

name: Langdon Hills Sweet Chestnuts
description: Mature sweet chestnut trees are abundant in the wooded sections of Westley Heights and Marks Hill.

name: Incredible Edible Basildon - Town Centre
description: Community planters located in the town centre featuring culinary herbs and seasonal greens.

name: Northlands Park Blackberries
description: Extensive blackberry bushes line the perimeters of the fishing lakes and woodland walks.

name: Noak Bridge Wild Garlic
description: The damp wooded edges near the Wash and local nature reserve paths are hotspots for spring wild garlic.

name: Gloucester Park Elder
description: Abundant elder bushes for flowers and berries grow along the wilder park fringes near the sporting village.

name: Wickford Memorial Park Orchard
description: A community-planted orchard featuring a mix of apple, cherry, and plum trees.

name: Bowers Gifford Sloes
description: Blackthorn bushes lining the quiet lanes and field boundaries are perfect for autumn sloe gathering.

name: Kingswood Incredible Edible Planters
description: Community planters featuring hardy herbs and salad leaves near the local shops.

name: Laindon Common Hazelnuts
description: Hazel trees are found in the hedgerows and woodland copses across the common.

name: Pitsea Mount Wild Plums
description: Occasional wild plum and cherry trees can be found along the scrubland paths leading up the mount.

name: River Crouch Sea Beet (Fringe)
description: Wild sea beet can be gathered from the sea walls along the Crouch near Wickford's northern fringe.

name: Nevendon Park Rosehips
description: The wilder perimeter hedges provide a good crop of rosehips and hawthorn haws.

name: Eversley Wild Greens
description: Find wild sorrel and watermint in the damp green spaces bordering the industrial estates.
